  For a tournament T on n vertices with beta_1(T)=0:
  dim(Z_1) = dim(B_1) = rank(d2|_{Omega_2})
  For T\v: dim(Z_1(T\v)) = C(n-2,2), dim(B_1(T\v)) = C(n-2,2) - beta_1(T\v)

